import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, NavItem } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

export default class CustomNavbar extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Navbar default collapseOnSelect>
      <Navbar.Header>
        <Navbar.Brand>
          <Link to="/">Code Life</Link>
        </Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle />
      </Navbar.Header>
      <Navbar.Collapse>
          <Nav pullRight>
            <NavItem eventKey={1} componentClass={Link} to="/">
            Home
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={1} componentClass={Link} to="/about">
            About
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={1} componentClass={Link} to="/services">
            Services
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem eventKey={1} componentClass={Link} to="/contact">
            Contact
            </NavItem>
          </Nav>
      </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Navbar>
    )
  }
}
